{"tid":59680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老搭巴士必做三部曲！","createTime":"2016-12-30T00:01:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T05:58:54.000Z","uid":16672,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"305017f67b56a8c458b65d7052c93ea8e29d1992","tid":59680,"uid":16672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:01:59.000Z","msg":"1. 首先上到車一定要左揀右揀，通常坐低左之後都會唔滿意現狀，起碼要轉一次位先安樂！<br />\n<br />\n2. 將個冷氣出風位左撥右撥，開完又關關完再開，慌死吹到佢頭都甩咁，如果較極都唔滿意會重複步驟一！<br />\n<br />\n3. 幾經辛苦坐定之後，會拎個老鏈咁大既鈎黎鈎住自己袋橙或剛買完既餸，有時會鈎埋前座乘客件衫，通常廢老一句sorry都懶得講！<br />\n<br />\n認真見親人做以上既野都係廢老，絕少見過後生既做以上動作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad1107145e3febe4f98b92b2775b857bcd7ceea","tid":59680,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:11:09.000Z","msg":"獅子山下精神"},{"pid":"068c13d4e26ce03248186804c40c5fc57c24ea39","tid":59680,"uid":13205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:36:30.000Z","msg":"4. 明知自己行動不便都要上上層坐，準備落車嗰陣車未停定就落樓梯，最終因為突然剎車仆落樓梯爆頭死"},{"pid":"3f6ef8e58028e146eb5ef805911448a01579644a","tid":59680,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:38:18.000Z","msg":"5. 坐出面等人地坐唔到入面"},{"pid":"a145a94675cacc0788349d09de29b749b6868322","tid":59680,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:38:59.000Z","msg":"好撚鐘意大大聲講野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好心就戴個耳聾機啦"},{"pid":"ede05d40dd6edf96d8bee6a28110a36186510d7b","tid":59680,"uid":377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:39:14.000Z","msg":"14. 食橙"},{"pid":"04727457beae1cf696e2fcdb0bd396228fb34587","tid":59680,"uid":16672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:45:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>5. 坐出面等人地坐唔到入面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公道少少<br />\n呢個我見中年阿叔仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121f6f22d32b1f7bdfa2cd347f63d7081294f132","tid":59680,"uid":8572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:46:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>5. 坐出面等人地坐唔到入面</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n公道少少<br />\n呢個我見中年阿叔仲多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n通常我會坐入去☺"},{"pid":"e9d04d7e0655cb9b435cc8c691a68f6e12a0ca01","tid":59680,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:48:31.000Z","msg":"俾車錢俾成世"},{"pid":"94a94fc92a9bf8ec478caab800f3e7c9570c7520","tid":59680,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:50:18.000Z","msg":"打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9b6973d95937dd3677fc910db64beb7cd63a3ee","tid":59680,"uid":54046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:55:42.000Z","msg":"返工時間搭巴士, 係總站搭<br />\n有兩條隊,一條勁長既隊, 但保證有得坐<br />\n一條無咩人,好快上到車,但100%無得坐<br />\n個次個廢老排快排,見無得坐,走上上層企<br />\n仲要專登企我面前,同埋拎個勾出黎勾住我前面張椅,<br />\n要讓我就真係彩佢都傻啦<br />\n排慢隊讓比你排快隊?<br />\n最後有個女仔讓左比個廢老"},{"pid":"9464580d9f106252ec9d079c59161fc8af585574","tid":59680,"uid":67996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:59:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nd廢老應該係未撚學過排隊<br />\n有d仲會直接忽視條隊<br />\n係隊頭隔離自己開條專屬line<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一有車黎就狗衝上車"},{"pid":"3d30b5d2db543f3da208997a6a1fcd9d7c78cd4b","tid":59680,"uid":45613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T00:59:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打尖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6534058a887848cbac8fde361f755fe806febb92","tid":59680,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:07:35.000Z","msg":"如果係一班人一齊行動，通常上到車都會有條友大叫一句:&quot;煨~~大把位呀&quot; / &quot;煨~~冇晒位喇&quot;"},{"pid":"b8ab8a09b97dd1891d0c02c5901492d85d40b82e","tid":59680,"uid":30850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:08:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>返工時間搭巴士, 係總站搭<br />\n有兩條隊,一條勁長既隊, 但保證有得坐<br />\n一條無咩人,好快上到車,但100%無得坐<br />\n個次個廢老排快排,見無得坐,走上上層企<br />\n仲要專登企我面前,同埋拎個勾出黎勾住我前面張椅,<br />\n要讓我就真係彩佢都傻啦<br />\n排慢隊讓比你排快隊?<br />\n最後有個女仔讓左比個廢老</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班廢老真係好撚鍾意企上上層獻世"},{"pid":"3ef3e5ee41c54d01924f7c9c46984ac8db414e64","tid":59680,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:09:35.000Z","msg":"6.開大喇叭睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1954904ecaa9e3d68d6ef3d4994b585cc4ecc28d","tid":59680,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:09:38.000Z","msg":"上到車搵八達通"},{"pid":"bc4460cb97b5bc357a1f3293297478977d9e63e8","tid":59680,"uid":14738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:10:23.000Z","msg":"坐喺兩張凳中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6f51df37ebb5880684333e30eccd1e36044355","tid":59680,"uid":34602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:11:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4. 明知自己行動不便都要上上層坐，準備落車嗰陣車未停定就落樓梯，最終因為突然剎車仆落樓梯爆頭死</blockquote><br />\n唔會囉，會停定先落嫁，不過早一個站落，然後頂住等成班人落唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e103b7f1e1d83425f104c0bf8d16772eafeb4ece","tid":59680,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:11:53.000Z","msg":"剪手指甲呢"},{"pid":"b8da557ae49c54ea5cf958299d1da4eaa814fd84","tid":59680,"uid":68325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T01:14:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係一班人一齊行動，通常上到車都會有條友大叫一句:&quot;煨~~大把位呀&quot; / &quot;煨~~冇晒位喇&quot;</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有聲</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji